article_title: John Kasich’s Art of the Deal
article_text:
It is time to ask: Who is John Kasich?

By his own admission, Mr. Kasich is the man who never gets called on in the debates. He’s getting called on now.

In the most hectic primary contest ever, which began with 17 Republican candidates spilling off stages while debating each other in separate tiers, the governor from Ohio is one of the...
